I write from Peru, i just got my frank&#39;s box from ebay, i have been using it
for two days in different places, all of them illuminated, and no results i
got. But recently i&#39;ve gone to a uninhabited beach at night (complete
darkness) i know some people died drowned there, i said &quot;hello&quot; and i heard
a very clear &quot;hello&quot; from a young guy as answer, since this is the first
time i do this kind of things i got very scared and didn&#39;t continue with the
experiment.



1.-Could you confirm if it is usually better to use the frank&#39;s box in
places uninhabited, or maybe in places in absolutely darkness? The &quot;Hello&quot; I
heard was extremely clear, clearest than most of the results i got from
youtube or even this forum, could these features (uninhabited or darkness)
influence?





2.-I&#39;m engineer and the reason i use the frank&#39;s box is curiosity, morbid
and scientific at the same time. I understand there is no risk to use the
frank&#39;s box, which would be different to use the ouija which i know is
risky. Is this so? 







Regards





Gustavo Chumbes


